<p class="small-margin-before">CCM Hockey Stick played by the legendary forward Pavel Datsyuk with his personal autograph and accompanying photo of Pavel with this signed stick. The stick from the 4-x player of the NHL All Star Game and holder of  the “Toughest forward to play against” NHL title was donated by him to TokenStars Crypto Xmas Charity Auction in December 2017 and is a rare and desired memorabilia for a true hockey fan.</p>
